### 14. Final Rule

The provided reference article is the authoritative structure for future Learn Medicine pages.

Preserve:

* Exact class names
* Exact container hierarchy
* Header arrangement
* TOC placement
* Main content placement
* Section ID matching
* Back-home placement
* Footer class
* Script order

Only the article title, metadata, TOC entries, section IDs, clinical content, reading time, and references should change from article to article.
